	<div id="content" class="hfeed">
	<article class="post-638676 post type-post status-publish hentry category-financial-services category-private-equity category-real-estate category-retailleisure tag-appraisals-and-valuation-property tag-hudsons-bay-co tag-mortgages tag-real-estate-commercial tag-saks-fifth-avenue tag-shopping-and-retail des-appraisals-and-valuation-property des-mortgages des-real-estate-commercial des-shopping-and-retail org-hudsons-bay-co org-saks-fifth-avenue news_keywords-commercial-real-estate news_keywords-hudsons-bay news_keywords-mortgage-loan news_keywords-property-appraisals news_keywords-retail news_keywords-saks-fifth-avenue" id="post-638676">
	<header class="postHeader">
